These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lilac, fuchsia, light-blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, bus, quad-bike, tram
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bus and the person who likes lilac##2
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes brown##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Color   | light-blue         | lilac   | fuchsia | brown       |
| Transport      | tram | skateboard | quad-bike   | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, alhambra, davidoff
There 4 different types of food: peach, papaya, banana, cauliflower
1. the person eating cauliflower is between the alhambra-smoker and the person eating papaya##2
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Cigar         | oliveros | havana | alhambra | davidoff |
| Food   | papaya    | cauliflower   | peach | banana       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, backgammon, canasta
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person playing go##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing go is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Game          | canasta    | mah-jongg | go   | backgammon  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta   | hot-chocolate | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, dahlia, amaryllis, lily
House: palace, futuristic, townhouse, colonial
1. the futuristic house is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the palace house and the person who growslily##2
3. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Flower     | lily   | daffodil    | amaryllis       | dahlia   |
| House   | townhouse | colonial | palace | futuristic |

