.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, sunflower, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, september, october
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Flower   | poppy        | sunflower | bellflower  | marigold |
| Birthday      | september | february  | october | december    |

