.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
House: ranch-style, cottage, farmhouse, futuristic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, montecristo, tiparillo, prince
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the futuristic house is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
4. the cottage house is the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the farmhouse house is between the ranch-style house and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| House   | cottage     | farmhouse           | ranch-style | futuristic  |
| Cigar         | baccarat | prince | montecristo   | tiparillo |

