3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is between the person drinking iced-tea and the havana-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | bluemaster | dannemann | havana      |
| Beverage     | soy-milk | iced-tea    | sprite  | coffee |

