.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, sudoku, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, techno, metal
1. the fan indie is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the fan blues is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the fan techno##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
4. the fan indie is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | gardening | drawing | sudoku     | rock-climbing   |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | blues     | metal | indie |

