2. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| House         | wooden | modern | craftsman | townhouse |
| Food   | pomegranate         | pineapple       | eggplant    | watermelon         |

