.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
City: marseilles, prague, nizza, liverpool
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, poker, monopoly
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the person traveling to prague and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| City    | liverpool   | nizza      | prague   | marseilles  |
| Game   | monopoly | scrabble | poker | bridge |

