2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsorchid##2
3. the american is on the right of the turkish##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
