3. the person traveling to new-york is the polish##1
4. the spanish is the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the french##1
6. the person traveling to venice is between the indonesian and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
