1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes lilac is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who likes blue##2
3. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Color           | blue | lilac | amber | black     |
| Pet   | goldfish   | bird    | rabbit   | fish |

