.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, turquise, white, apricot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, golf, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who likes white is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who likes turquise##2
4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | amber | turquise | white | apricot |
| Sport     | biathlon     | cycling   | climbing | golf  |

