1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
3. the person watching horror movies is between the person who likes mauve and the person watching musical movies##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Movie-Genre       | disaster | horror | musical | sports |
| Color   | mauve    | aquamarine  | blood-red    | turquise       |

