3. the person traveling to london is the fan metal##1
4. the fan electronic is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to colone##2
5. the person traveling to colone is the fan pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City   | london   | hannover   | prague | colone |
| Music-Genre         | metal | dubstep | electronic     | pop    |

