.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, iced-tea, lemonade
House: wooden, tower, gothic-revival, colonial
1. the tower house is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the wooden house and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | lemonade     | soy-milk | fanta |
| House     | tower | colonial | gothic-revival       | wooden     |

 